TEXT.S: Skënder Sallaku ryax 25, 1 byacing 1935 kawas qu hintgan nya ru tehuk ryax 11, 2 byacing kawas 2014 qu hinqilan nya, 79 kawas qu qinnxan nya. hiya ga Albania blaq balay psyaqan pgeki na squliq. lalu nya ga hcyux naha sr'xun ska Albania (People's Artist of Albania). minnagal sa pciriq squ pkyap squ Albania, hiya wal magal champion. sasan nqu ryax 11, 2 byacing, ru kawas te 2014 lga, wayal mhuqil squ Albania Tirane la. mnaki squ bih nya kwara qu qutux ngasal nya.
